body.description: Feel spring in the air with our complex blend of Glade Joyful Citrus & Daisies plug in air freshener for home. Crafted by master perfumers with notes of pink grapefruit, daisies and golden raspberries. Put a pep in your step with our scent diffuser and change the mood with 2x more adjustability (vs. previous Glade warmer). Express your mood with electric oil diffuser in Joyful Citrus & Daisies fragrance. Simply remove the cap from the refill and insert it into Glade plug in warmer. Plug the warmer into an outlet and adjust the level of fragrance to create the mood you want. Bring out your best self with Glade's plugin air freshener and fragrance infused with essential oils.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The Glade PlugIns Refills Air Freshener is a game-changer for creating a welcoming atmosphere in my home. The scented and essential oils blend seamlessly to deliver a refreshing and long-lasting fragrance, instantly transforming any room, including bathrooms, into a pleasant space. The variety of scents available caters to diverse preferences, allowing for a personalized aromatic experience. The ease of use with the plug-in design is convenient, providing a continuous burst of delightful fragrance without any effort. I appreciate the versatility and reliability of these refills, making them an essential addition to my home for maintaining a consistently inviting and pleasant environment. If you're looking for a reliable and effective air freshener, Glade PlugIns Refills are a fantastic choice.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Festive Resurgence: Glade Plugin Pine & Cedar Refills Save the Day!
reviews.reviewText: As someone who has always cherished the nostalgic scent of a real Christmas tree, I found myself in a bit of a conundrum this year when I opted for the convenience of a fake tree. The absence of that familiar aroma left me feeling a bit blue during the holiday season. Enter the Glade Plugin Pine & Cedar refills, a true game-changer that not only rescued my festive spirit but exceeded my expectations.The first thing that struck me was the uncanny resemblance of these plugins to the enchanting scent of a real Christmas tree. The combination of pine and cedar is nothing short of magical, instantly transporting me to a winter wonderland filled with the unmistakable fragrance of fresh evergreens. The pine scent is robust and authentic, evoking the sensation of being surrounded by a forest of Christmas trees. It's like bringing the great outdoors inside, infusing my home with the festive spirit I thought I had lost.What sets these refills apart is their ability to capture the essence of Christmas and transform any space into a holiday haven. The fragrance is not overpowering but lingers delicately, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere that resonates with the joy of the season. The convenience of the Glade plugin is also a huge plus, effortlessly spreading the festive scent throughout my home without any hassle.In conclusion, Glade Plugin Pine & Cedar refills have been a holiday savior for me. If, like me, you miss the delightful scent of a real Christmas tree, these plugins are a must-try. They've turned my artificial tree experience around, and I wholeheartedly recommend them to anyone looking to infuse their home with the heartwarming aroma of the holiday season. Say goodbye to the artificial blues and hello to the authentic joy of Christmas with Glade!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Our New Favorite Fragrance
reviews.reviewText: I have used glade products for years especially plug-ins. And have never been a fan of their original vanilla, it smelled too sweet for me to have all over my home. I have tried so many scents some I have liked, but this one the Vanilla Embrace is perfect it’s a light scent that also makes the place smell fresh, welcoming and homey without being overpowering.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great scent for short term usage
reviews.reviewText: In my opinion, this is one of the best-smelling scents this brand makes. It is a great option for a Fall scent around the house. I have this product being used in my living room. For the first few days, the scent is strong and noticeable. After about 10 or so days, the scent is practically gone. Overall, great product, I just wished it lasted longer!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Smell, but Keep it Low!
reviews.reviewText: Finally! My house can smell like pumpkin pie! I love this fall scent, however, don't set your plugin to max when you plug this scent in or it smells absolutely WAY too strong. It will attack your nose and smell like a barbeque from hell. After I set my plugins to low it was the perfect level and resumed its sweet fall scenting.
